https://askubuntu.com/questions/37824/what-is-the-best-way-to-configure-a-thinkpads-trackpoint/37841#37841

# Jugar con los valores de :
/sys/devices/platform/i8042/serio1/serio2/sensitivity
/sys/devices/platform/i8042/serio1/serio2/speed

# Crear y editar
/etc/udev/rules.d/trackpoint.rules

